level.heading: License requirements for physician office laboratories.

level.text: For temporary (90 day) amendment of section, see § 3(dd)(2) of Streamlining Regulation Emergency Act of 2003 (D.C. Act 15-145, August 11, 2003, 50 DCR 6896).
